column2: The information provided in our listings is based on publicly available data from providers or from third-party sources, like construction applications, permits, press releases, satellite images and Aterio's own research.
Many Data Center Providers do not publicly disclose all data center locations or details on square feet or MW capacity.
As a result, some locations may be incorrect, outdated, or incomplete. Some power demand figures and facility details are also estimates based on these sources and may vary from actual values.
